.H2 Bin
.H3 Troff Companions
.PP
Troff has been made to be used within tubes. It works with
pre-processors, post-processors and filters. A lot of filters
exist since the 70's. Some of them needed some enhancement
to be used with \*Iutmac\*I, some others needed to be created.
.
.
.
.
.H3 Ugrind
.PP
\*IUgrind\*I is an awfull hack of \*Ivfontedpr\*I, the
programm which makes the hard work of the mostly forgotten
\*Ivgrind\*I preprocessor: it highlights code in troff
sources. \*IVfontedpr\*I doesn't handle variables, troff
source nor color, \*IUgrind\*I does all that, and is easier
to use. It is written in C, and is probably the lightest
tool one can find for this task.
.PL
See the following files:
.LT ugrind ,
.LU man/ugrind.html
.LT "isc license" ,
.LU man/isc.html
.LT "bsd4 license" ,
.LU man/bsd4.html
.LT "cddl license" .
.LU man/cddl.html
.git ugrind
.
.
.
.H3 Idx
\*IIdx\*I build, repair, format, and handle index files. It
has been made to automatically index a troff document, but
it also provides option to be used as an helper tool to
manually index a book, and work with index files. \*Iidx\*I
is a \*Ishell\*I and \*Iawk\*I script.
.PL
See the following files:
.LT idx ,
.LU http://utroff.org/man/idx.html
.LT license ,
.LU http://utroff.org/man/bsd2.html
.git idx
.
.H3 Refer
.PP
\*IRefer\*I is a small hack of the venerable \*Irefer\*I, as
found in the
.LT "\*Iheirloom-doctools\*I"
.LU http://heirloom.sourceforge.net/doctools.html
archive.
This modification of \*IRefer\*I uses strings to define small
capitals, makes a difference between lastname and firstname in author
and editor fields, add support for multiple editors, and offers an
option to sort the bibliography database in the order defined by the
\*Iiso-690\*I bibliography standart.
.PL
See the following files:
.LT hunt ,
.LU man/hunt.html
.LT inv ,
.LU man/inv.html
.LT mkey ,
.LU man/mkey.html
.LT referformat ,
.LU man/referformat.html
.LT refer ,
.LU man/refer.html
.LT sortbib ,
.LU man/sortbib.html
.LT "license bsd4" ,
.LU man/bsd4.html
.LT "license cddl" ,
.LU man/cddl.html
.git refer
.
