.H3 Tchars
.PP
\*ITchars\*I translate an ascii coded text to complex utf-8
characters. Actually, it can only translate a simple sort of
beta-code to polytonic greek.
.PL
See the following files:
.LT tchars ,
.LU http://utroff.org/man/tchars.html
.LT license ,
.LU http://utroff.org/man/bsd2.html
.git tchars
.
